底特律 DJ 迈克·布朗去世后哀悼https://www.nme.com/news/music/tributes-paid-after-death-of-detroit-dj-mike-brown-3572379?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=tributes-paid-after-death-of-底特律 DJ 迈克·布朗Will RichardsWed, 17 Jan 2024 14:15:26 +0000 Music NewsNews.. https://www.nme.com/?p=3572379 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="NME 突发新闻" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>布朗去年推出了癌症治疗众筹页面</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tributes-paid-after-death-of-detroit-dj-mike-brown-3572379">底特律 DJ Mike Brown 去世后的悼念帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="NME 突发新闻" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>底特律颇具影响力的 DJ 迈克·布朗 (Mike Brown) 因癌症诊断去世。</p><p>据报道，这一消息是由<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C2GT73tv-_B/?img_index=3" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">底特律 Charivari</a>音乐节宣布的，并得到了他的朋友 Pat Lee 的证实。</p><p>去年，李为粉丝建立了一个众筹页面，为这位 DJ 的癌症治疗提供资金。</p><p>尽管没有透露官方死因，但李说布朗于 1 月 14 日星期日去世，当时正在接受肾透析并等待器官移植。</p><p>布朗去世后，GoFundMe 页面现已重新启动，以帮助他的家人支付医疗费用和丧葬费用。</p><p>该页面上的一篇帖子称布朗为“通过友谊、音乐、支持文化对抗分歧，以及最重要的是通过社区创造平衡，帮助塑造底特律灵魂的拼图中的一块。”</p><p>关于他的病情，它补充道：“在与癌症作斗争的过程中，他一直在肾透析中挣扎，所有人都祈祷进行移植。看到这位坚强的人，他是所有有幸认识这位绅士的人的朋友，也是许多始终把自己放在一边的人的家人，看到他让很多人心碎。他更关心他89岁的父亲。”</p><p><a href="https://www.gofundme.com/f/cbgwtw-beautiful-soul" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里支持 GoFundMe</a> 。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C2GT73tv-_B/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-